description:
This is a 19 minute workout called 'Guided Breathing: Awaken Your Nervous System' from the channel Kitaro Waga.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Don't do this breathwork in water or when driving.
